{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "792892c1-997e-4a7f-91fc-0ce92e682be4",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Nemeses Corridor",
      "effect": "You can target 1 of your banished monsters, except \"Nemeses Corridor\"; Special Summon this card from your hand, and if you do, shuffle that target into the Deck. You can target 1 of your banished \"Nemeses\" monsters, except \"Nemeses Corridor\"; add it to your hand. You can only use each effect of \"Nemeses Corridor\" once per turn."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Corridor N\u00e9m\u00e9ses",
      "effect": "Vous pouvez cibler 1 de vos monstres bannis (\"Corridor N\u00e9m\u00e9ses\" exclu) ; Invoquez Sp\u00e9cialement cette carte depuis votre main, et si vous le faites, m\u00e9langez la cible dans le Deck. Vous pouvez cibler 1 de vos monstres \"N\u00e9m\u00e9ses\" bannis (\"Corridor N\u00e9m\u00e9ses\" exclu) ; ajoutez-le \u00e0 votre main. Vous ne pouvez utiliser chaque effet de \"Corridor N\u00e9m\u00e9ses\" qu'une fois par tour."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Todfeind Korridor",
      "effect": "Du kannst 1 deiner verbannten Monster w\u00e4hlen, au\u00dfer \u201eTodfeind Korridor\u201c; beschw\u00f6re diese Karte als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung von deiner Hand und falls du dies tust, mische jenes gew\u00e4hlte Ziel ins Deck. Du kannst 1 deiner verbannten \u201eTodfeind\u201c-Monster w\u00e4hlen, au\u00dfer \u201eTodfeind Korridor\u201c; f\u00fcge es deiner Hand hinzu. Du kannst jeden Effekt von \u201eTodfeind Korridor\u201c nur einmal pro Spielzug verwenden."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Nemeses Corridoio",
      "effect": "Puoi scegliere come bersaglio 1 dei tuoi mostri banditi, eccetto \"Nemeses Corridoio\"; Evoca Specialmente questa carta dalla tua mano e, se lo fai, mischia quel bersaglio nel Deck. Puoi scegliere come bersaglio 1 dei tuoi mostri \"Nemeses\" banditi, eccetto \"Nemeses Corridoio\"; aggiungilo alla tua mano. Puoi utilizzare ogni effetto di \"Nemeses Corridoio\" una sola volta per turno."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Corredor N\u00eameses",
      "effect": "Voc\u00ea pode escolher 1 dos seus monstros banidos, exceto \"Corredor N\u00eameses\"; Invoque este card por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial da sua m\u00e3o e, se isso acontecer, embaralhe o alvo no Deck. Voc\u00ea pode escolher 1 dos seus monstros \"N\u00eameses\" banidos, exceto \"Corredor N\u00eameses\"; adicione-o \u00e0 sua m\u00e3o. Voc\u00ea s\u00f3 pode usar cada efeito de \"Corredor N\u00eameses\" uma vez por turno."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "N\u00e9meses Corredor",
      "effect": "Puedes seleccionar 1 de tus monstruos desterrados, excepto \"N\u00e9meses Corredor\"; Invoca esta carta de Modo Especial desde tu mano y, si lo haces, baraja ese objetivo al Deck. Puedes seleccionar 1 de tus monstruos \"N\u00e9meses\" desterrados, excepto \"N\u00e9meses Corredor\"; a\u00f1\u00e1delo a tu mano. S\u00f3lo puedes usar cada efecto de \"N\u00e9meses Corredor\" una vez por turno."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30cd\u30e1\u30b7\u30b9\u30fb\u30b3\u30ea\u30c9\u30fc",
      "effect": "\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u540d\u306e\u2460\u2461\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u306f\u305d\u308c\u305e\u308c\uff11\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\uff11\u5ea6\u3057\u304b\u4f7f\u7528\u3067\u304d\u306a\u3044\u3002\u2460\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u624b\u672d\u306b\u5b58\u5728\u3059\u308b\u5834\u5408\u3001\u300c\u30cd\u30e1\u30b7\u30b9\u30fb\u30b3\u30ea\u30c9\u30fc\u300d\u4ee5\u5916\u306e\u81ea\u5206\u306e\u9664\u5916\u72b6\u614b\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5bfe\u8c61\u3068\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u3092\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3057\u3001\u5bfe\u8c61\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3092\u30c7\u30c3\u30ad\u306b\u623b\u3059\u3002\u2461\uff1a\u300c\u30cd\u30e1\u30b7\u30b9\u30fb\u30b3\u30ea\u30c9\u30fc\u300d\u4ee5\u5916\u306e\u81ea\u5206\u306e\u9664\u5916\u72b6\u614b\u306e\u300c\u30cd\u30e1\u30b7\u30b9\u300d\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5bfe\u8c61\u3068\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3092\u624b\u672d\u306b\u52a0\u3048\u308b\u3002"
